  </section>

  <%# Phase 20260608 commerce-admin-selector-readonly-preview-implementation-a
      registry-global read-only commerce links / affiliate references preview
      per docs/20260608-commerce-admin-selector-preanalysis.md §6 / §10
        + docs/20260608-commerce-admin-selector-ui-source-preanalysis.md §5 / §6 / §7
      - DATA SOURCE = production settings.commerceLinks（loader unwrap array）；registry empty → empty-state
      - read-only / no Apply / no registry write / no markdown write / no middleware / no admin-write-cli
