      - role enum = C8 mirror（authoring guidance；role 仍 recommended-but-optional；C7 missing-role deferred）
  %>
  <%
    var commercePreview = (typeof commerceLinksPreview === 'object' && commerceLinksPreview)
      ? commerceLinksPreview : { rows: [], count: 0 };
    var commerceRows = Array.isArray(commercePreview.rows) ? commercePreview.rows : [];
    var commerceRoles = (typeof allowedCommerceRoles !== 'undefined' && Array.isArray(allowedCommerceRoles))
      ? allowedCommerceRoles : [];
  %>
  <section id="commerce" style="margin: 1.5rem 0; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #c5d6e8; border-radius: 4px; background: #f3f7fc;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #2c5282; border-bottom: 1px solid #c5d6e8; padding-bottom: 0.4rem;">commerce links / affiliate references preview (read-only)</h3>
    <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.85em; line-height: 1.6;">
      🔒 Read-only preview — no Admin Apply · no registry write · no markdown write · no middleware · no admin-write-cli.
      資料來源為 production <code>settings.commerceLinks</code>（<code>content/settings/commerce-links.json</code>）；
      不讀 <code>_sample.commerce-links.json</code>、不讀 validation overlay / fixture、不 auto-promote sample。
      僅顯示安全欄位（ref machine key / active status / 公開 display label / has replacement target）；
      不顯示 targetUrl / tracking URL / internalLabel / merchant id / token / credential。
      role 為 <strong>recommended-but-optional</strong>；C7（missing-role required）目前 <strong>deferred</strong>，下方 role enum 僅為 authoring guidance。
