    </div>

    <%# Phase 20260608-night-1 commerce-admin-copyable-yaml-snippet-source-only-a
        per docs/20260608-commerce-admin-copyable-yaml-snippet-preanalysis.md §5 / §6 / §7 / §8 / §10 / §14
        - 純 authoring helper：產生可手動複製、貼進 .md frontmatter 之 affiliate.links YAML fragment
        - read-only：不自動寫 .md / registry / fs / fetch / middleware / admin-write-cli
        - snippet 只輸出：ref（linkId machine key）+ role（enum；空則省略 key 避免 C8 誤觸）+ labelOverride（空則省略）
        - 永不輸出：targetUrl / internalLabel / tracking URL / token / credential / merchant id / networkKey
        - registry empty → 不渲染 snippet UI（既有 empty-state 已說明）
