  <%# Phase 20260615-night-1-admin-ia-shell-implementation-a：Posts section anchor + 介紹 -%>
  <h2 id="posts" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #1f2d3d; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 0.35rem;">Posts <span class="section-tag tag-readonly">read-only</span></h2>
  <p class="section-lede" style="color: #555; font-size: 0.88em; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">列出 <code>content/{github,blogger}/posts/*.md</code> 之全部文章（含 draft）。可搜尋 / 篩選 / 排序；點 row 展開 detail。本表不提供新增 / 編輯 / 刪除 / 發布按鈕；任何寫入路徑仍只有 CLI（<code>npm run admin:write</code>，目前對 content dormant）。</p>
  <%# Phase 20260615-night-3-admin-posts-index-readonly-derive-fields-a：generation timestamp banner
      - 顯示本次 admin render 之 builtAt（ISO 8601，由 build-github 傳入）
      - 不寫入 source / production content；不 commit .cache / dist；本欄純頁面 metadata
      - 重新整理 dev server 會重跑 predev 並更新此 timestamp -%>
  <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em; margin: -0.5rem 0 0.75rem;">
    <strong>generatedAt / lastDerivedAt：</strong>
    <span class="mono"><%= builtAt %></span>
    · 本次 admin 頁所有 derived 欄位皆於此時間從 frontmatter / settings 推導；重新整理 dev server（<code>npm run dev</code>）會重新 derive。
  </p>

  <%# Phase 20260617-am-admin-r3-health-legend-missing-fields-dedup-implementation-a:
      Legend Opt-A —— page-level health vocabulary legend（只此 1 處，不在每篇 detail panel ×11 重複）。
      區分 ground truth（validator/report）vs admin derived read-only hint；不寫「自動修正」/「應改為 X」；沿用既有 .admin-governance-note class（零新 CSS）。 -%>
  <aside class="admin-governance-note" aria-label="health vocabulary legend" style="margin: 0 0 0.85rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.8rem; background: #f4f7fb; border-left: 3px solid #6c7a89; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.86em; line-height: 1.55;">
    <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>健康訊號讀法（read-only）：</strong></p>
    <ul style="margin: 0.3rem 0 0; padding-left: 1.2rem;">
      <li><strong>Validation warnings</strong>（detail panel → Readiness）：來自 <code>npm run validate:content</code> 之 report，為 validator / report <strong>ground truth</strong>（僅掃 ready/published；draft 顯「未驗證」非 0）。</li>
      <li><strong>Completeness / Missing fields</strong>：admin loader 依 frontmatter / settings 推導之 <strong>read-only 提示</strong>，<strong>不等於 build blocker</strong>。</li>
      <li><strong>Governance signals</strong>（<code>gov</code> badge）：taxonomy 治理推導之 <strong>read-only 提示</strong>，<strong>不等於 validator warning 計數</strong>（universe 不同：governance 含 draft；validator 僅 ready/published）。</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin: 0.3rem 0 0; color: #6c7a89;">Admin 不自動修改文章 / <code>categories.json</code> / <code>tags.json</code>；是否調整由人眼判斷後另開 phase。<code>npm run validate:content</code> 仍為 ground truth。</p>
  </aside>

  <% if (posts.length === 0) { %>
    <p class="empty">無 posts 可顯示（content/{github,blogger}/posts/*.md 為空）</p>
  <% } else { %>
  <div class="controls">
    <label>
      🔎
      <input type="search" id="admin-search" placeholder="搜尋 title / slug / category / tags" autocomplete="off">
    </label>
    <label>
      篩選：
      <select id="admin-filter">
        <option value="all">all</option>
        <optgroup label="status">
          <option value="status:ready">status: ready</option>
          <option value="status:draft">status: draft</option>
          <option value="status:published">status: published</option>
        </optgroup>
        <optgroup label="channel">
          <option value="blogger:enabled">Blogger enabled</option>
          <option value="blogger:disabled">Blogger disabled</option>
          <option value="github:enabled">GitHub enabled</option>
          <option value="github:disabled">GitHub disabled</option>
        </optgroup>
        <%# Phase 20260523-pm-3-admin-a1-source-site-filter-optgroup-a: sourceSite filter optgroup
            （per docs/admin-overview-audit-20260523.md §10.1 A1）；sourceSite 為文章原始檔位置
            content/{site}/posts/，僅 2 值（blogger / github），與 channel 之 publishTargets enabled
            概念不同。emoji 對齊 URLs 欄之既有 📘 / 🐙 convention。 -%>
        <optgroup label="sourceSite (來源)">
          <option value="sourceSite:blogger">📘 sourceSite: blogger</option>
          <option value="sourceSite:github">🐙 sourceSite: github</option>
        </optgroup>
        <optgroup label="completeness">
          <option value="completeness:seo-missing">SEO missing</option>
          <option value="completeness:fb-missing">FB missing</option>
          <option value="completeness:url-missing">publishedUrl missing</option>
          <option value="completeness:categoryTags-missing">category/tags missing</option>
          <option value="completeness:fbPublished-missing">FB published missing</option>
        </optgroup>
        <%# Phase 20260523-pm-5-admin-a2-fb-badge-filter-optgroup-a: fbBadge filter optgroup
            （per docs/admin-overview-audit-20260523.md §10.1 A2）；fbBadge 為 FB sidecar
            derived 狀態（per docs/fb-sidecar-metadata-pre-analysis.md §6.2 + load-admin-posts.js
            deriveFbBadge）；4 well-known values（none / disabled / posted / ready）；
            passthrough status（draft / archived 等）user 仍可透過 search 或 completeness filter
            觸及，本批不展開以維持 zero-cost。 -%>
        <optgroup label="fbBadge (FB 狀態)">
          <option value="fbBadge:posted">FB badge: posted (已發文)</option>
          <option value="fbBadge:ready">FB badge: ready (待發文)</option>
          <option value="fbBadge:none">FB badge: none (無 sidecar)</option>
          <option value="fbBadge:disabled">FB badge: disabled (sidecar enabled=false)</option>
        </optgroup>
        <optgroup label="contentKind">
          <option value="kind:post">contentKind: post</option>
          <option value="kind:page">contentKind: page</option>
          <option value="kind:tech-note">contentKind: tech-note</option>
          <option value="kind:book-review">contentKind: book-review</option>
          <option value="kind:download">contentKind: download</option>
        </optgroup>
        <%# Phase 20260522-night-3-c: category optgroup（來源 posts 中實際出現之 p.category；無資料時不渲染） -%>
        <% if (uniqueCategories.length > 0) { %>
        <optgroup label="Category">
          <% uniqueCategories.forEach(function(c) { %>
          <option value="category:<%= c %>">category: <%= c %></option>
          <% }); %>
        </optgroup>
        <% } %>
        <%# Phase 20260522-night-3-c: series optgroup（來源 posts 中實際 p.series.id|slug；當前 loader 未處理 series；無資料時不渲染） -%>
        <% if (uniqueSeries.length > 0) { %>
        <optgroup label="Series">
          <% uniqueSeries.forEach(function(s) { %>
          <option value="series:<%= s %>">series: <%= s %></option>
          <% }); %>
        </optgroup>
        <% } %>
        <%# Phase 20260617-am-admin-validator-state-filter-chip-list-implementation-a：
            minimal Phase B v1 — 4 個 read-only validation filter；對齊 row data-validation-state；
            純消費 p.validationReport（pm-18）；不引 per-post prescription / 不引 auto-fix。 -%>
        <optgroup label="validation">
          <option value="validation:issues">validation: issues (errors &gt; 0 或 warnings &gt; 0)</option>
          <option value="validation:clean">validation: clean (matched &amp; 0/0)</option>
          <option value="validation:excluded">validation: excluded (draft/archived；不在 validator universe)</option>
          <option value="validation:no-report">validation: no report (report 缺檔 / 不可用)</option>
        </optgroup>
      </select>
    </label>
    <%# Phase 20260522-night-3-d: basic sort dropdown；3 選項；default publishedAt desc 對齊 loader 初始排序 -%>
    <label>
      排序：
      <select id="admin-sort">
        <option value="publishedAt-desc">publishedAt desc</option>
        <option value="updatedAt-desc">updatedAt desc</option>
        <option value="title-asc">title asc</option>
        <%# Phase 20260523-pm-16-admin-fbpostedat-sort-a: 補 fbPostedAt desc 排序選項；per docs/admin-overview-audit-20260523.md §10.1 B4；row 對應 attr 為 data-fb-posted-at -%>
        <option value="fbPostedAt-desc">fbPostedAt desc</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <button type="button" id="admin-show-all-toggle" style="padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem; border: 1px solid #bbb; border-radius: 3px; background: #fff; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.9em;" hidden>Show all</button>
    <span class="visible-count" id="admin-visible-count">showing <%= total %> of <%= total %> matched (<%= total %> total)</span>
  </div>

  <table id="admin-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>id / title</th>
        <th class="col-narrow">kind / status</th>
        <th>category / tags</th>
        <th>Blogger</th>
        <th>GitHub</th>
        <th class="col-narrow">Completeness</th>
        <th class="col-urls">URLs</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% posts.forEach(function(p, idx) {
        const searchBlob = [p.title, p.titleEn, p.slug, p.category, p.id, ...(p.tags || [])].join(' ').toLowerCase();
        const statusVal = (p.status === 'ready' || p.status === 'draft' || p.status === 'published') ? p.status : 'other';
        // Phase 20260617-am-admin-validator-state-filter-chip-list-implementation-a：
        //   - 純消費 p.validationReport.state（pm-18 loader derive；不重算 rule；不混 governance）
        //   - matched + (errorCount>0 || warningCount>0) → 'issues'
        //   - matched + 0/0（理論上不發生，pm-18 derive 在 entry 缺時走 'clean'）→ defensive 視為 'clean'
        //   - status-excluded → 'excluded'；no-report → 'no-report'；clean → 'clean'；unexpected → 'unknown'
        const vrState = (p.validationReport && p.validationReport.state) || 'no-report';
        let validationStateAttr;
        if (vrState === 'no-report') validationStateAttr = 'no-report';
        else if (vrState === 'status-excluded') validationStateAttr = 'excluded';
        else if (vrState === 'clean') validationStateAttr = 'clean';
        else if (vrState === 'matched') {
          const ec = (p.validationReport && p.validationReport.errorCount) || 0;
          const wc = (p.validationReport && p.validationReport.warningCount) || 0;
          validationStateAttr = (ec > 0 || wc > 0) ? 'issues' : 'clean';
        } else validationStateAttr = 'unknown';
      %>
      <tr class="post-row"
          data-idx="<%= idx %>"
          data-search="<%= searchBlob %>"
          data-status="<%= statusVal %>"
          data-blogger="<%= p.blogger.enabled ? 'enabled' : 'disabled' %>"
          data-github="<%= p.github.enabled ? 'enabled' : 'disabled' %>"
          data-seo="<%= p.completeness.seo %>"
          data-fb="<%= p.completeness.fb %>"
          data-url="<%= p.completeness.url %>"
          data-cat-tags="<%= p.completeness.categoryTags %>"
          data-fb-published="<%= p.completeness.fbPublished %>"
          data-content-kind="<%= p.contentKind || '' %>"
          data-source-site="<%= p.sourceSite || '' %>"
          data-fb-badge="<%= p.fbBadge || '' %>"
          data-category="<%= p.category || '' %>"
          data-series="<%= (p.series && (p.series.id || p.series.slug)) || '' %>"
          data-published-at="<%= p.publishedAt || '' %>"
          data-updated-at="<%= p.updatedAt || p.publishedAt || '' %>"
          data-fb-posted-at="<%= p.fbPostedAt || '' %>"
          data-validation-state="<%= validationStateAttr %>"
          data-title="<%= p.title || '' %>">
        <td>
          <% if (p.title) { %><strong><%= p.title %></strong><% } else { %><span class="empty">(empty)</span><% } %>
          <span class="toggle-hint"></span>
          <% if (p.titleEn) { %><br><span class="text-muted"><%= p.titleEn %></span><% } %>
          <br><span class="mono text-muted"><%= p.id || '(empty)' %></span>
          <br><span class="mono text-muted">slug: <%= p.slug || '(empty)' %></span>
          <% var pRel = formatRelativeDate(p.publishedAt); %>
          <br><span class="mono text-muted" title="<%= p.publishedSource ? 'source: ' + p.publishedSource : 'no publishedAt source' %>">published: <%= p.publishedAt || '(empty)' %><% if (pRel) { %> · <%= pRel %><% } %><% if (p.publishedSource) { %> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.85em;">(<%= p.publishedSource %>)</span><% } %></span>
        </td>
        <td class="col-narrow">
          <% if (p.contentKind) { %>
            <span class="badge b-info"><%= p.contentKind %></span>
          <% } else { %>
            <span class="badge b-missing">no kind</span>
          <% } %>
          <br>
          <% if (p.status === 'ready') { %><span class="badge b-ready">ready</span>
          <% } else if (p.status === 'draft' || p.draft) { %><span class="badge b-draft">draft</span>
          <% } else if (p.status === 'published') { %><span class="badge b-published">published</span>
          <% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing"><%= p.status || 'no status' %></span><% } %>
          <br><span class="text-muted mono">src: <%= p.sourceSite %></span>
          <%# Phase 20260520-fb-p5-a：FB sidecar derived status badge（per docs/fb-sidecar-metadata-pre-analysis.md §6.2） -%>
          <%
            var fbBadgeClass = 'b-info';
            if (p.fbBadge === 'posted') { fbBadgeClass = 'b-published'; }
            else if (p.fbBadge === 'ready') { fbBadgeClass = 'b-ready'; }
            else if (p.fbBadge === 'none' || p.fbBadge === 'disabled') { fbBadgeClass = 'b-info'; }
            else { fbBadgeClass = 'b-draft'; }
          -%>
          <br><span class="badge <%= fbBadgeClass %>" title="FB sidecar derived status；per Phase 20260520-fb-p5-a；none=檔案不存在 / disabled=enabled=false / posted=已發文 / ready=已啟用待發 / 其他=照 status 顯示">FB: <%= p.fbBadge %></span>
        </td>
        <td>
          <% if (p.category) { %><span class="badge b-info"><%= p.category %></span>
          <% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing">no category</span><% } %>
          <% if (p.tags.length > 0) { %><br>
            <% p.tags.forEach(function(t) { %><span class="badge b-tag">#<%= t %></span><% }); %>
          <% } else { %><br><span class="badge b-missing">no tags</span><% } %>
        </td>
        <td>
          <% if (p.blogger.enabled) { %>
            <span class="badge b-ok">enabled</span>
            <% if (p.blogger.mode) { %><span class="badge b-info"><%= p.blogger.mode %></span><% } %>
            <br>
            <% if (p.blogger.publishedUrl) { %><span class="badge b-published">published</span>
            <% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing">no URL</span><% } %>
          <% } else { %><span class="badge b-info">disabled</span><% } %>
        </td>
        <td>
          <% if (p.github.enabled) { %>
            <span class="badge b-ok">enabled</span>
            <% if (p.github.mode) { %><span class="badge b-info"><%= p.github.mode %></span><% } %>
          <% } else { %><span class="badge b-info">disabled</span><% } %>
        </td>
        <td class="col-narrow">
          <span class="badge <%= p.completeness.seo === 'ok' ? 'b-ok' : 'b-missing' %>">SEO <%= p.completeness.seo %></span><br>
          <span class="badge <%= p.completeness.fb === 'ok' ? 'b-ok' : 'b-missing' %>">FB <%= p.completeness.fb %></span><br>
          <span class="badge <%= p.completeness.blogger === 'ok' ? 'b-ok' : 'b-missing' %>">Blogger <%= p.completeness.blogger %></span><br>
          <span class="badge <%= p.completeness.github === 'ok' ? 'b-ok' : 'b-missing' %>">GitHub <%= p.completeness.github %></span><br>
          <span class="badge <%= p.completeness.url === 'ok' ? 'b-ok' : 'b-missing' %>">URL <%= p.completeness.url %></span><br>
          <span class="badge <%= p.completeness.categoryTags === 'ok' ? 'b-ok' : 'b-missing' %>">cat/tags <%= p.completeness.categoryTags %></span><br>
          <span class="badge <%= p.completeness.fbPublished === 'ok' ? 'b-ok' : 'b-missing' %>" title="FB disabled 或文章尚未 published → ok；文章已 published 且 FB enabled=true 且 fbPostUrl 空 → missing">FB pub <%= p.completeness.fbPublished %></span>
          <%# Phase 20260615-night-3-admin-posts-index-readonly-derive-fields-a：compact readiness badges
              - 只是既有 derived 物件之短摘要；點 row 展開可見 full detail 與 source / note
              - title attr 明示「derived；查 detail 看 source」-%>
          <br><span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.74em; display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.25rem;">readiness ▾</span><br>
          <% var arPages = (p.adsenseReadiness && p.adsenseReadiness.pagesBlockCount) || 0; %>
          <% var arBlogger = (p.adsenseReadiness && p.adsenseReadiness.bloggerBlockCount) || 0; %>
          <% var ga4Indexable = p.ga4Readiness && p.ga4Readiness.surfaceIndexable; %>
          <span class="badge <%= arPages > 0 ? 'b-ok' : 'b-info' %>" title="settings-resolved AdSense blocks on pages surface (derived)">ads:pages <%= arPages %></span>
          <span class="badge <%= arBlogger > 0 ? 'b-ok' : 'b-info' %>" title="settings-resolved AdSense blocks on blogger surface (derived)">ads:blogger <%= arBlogger %></span><br>
          <% if (ga4Indexable === true) { %><span class="badge b-ok" title="seo.indexing implies indexable">idx ok</span>
          <% } else if (ga4Indexable === false) { %><span class="badge b-info" title="seo.indexing = noindex-*">noindex</span>
          <% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing" title="seo.indexing invalid or unknown">idx ?</span><% } %>
          <% if (p.navReadiness && p.navReadiness.eligibleForNav) { %><span class="badge b-ok" title="github.enabled=true → eligible for prev/next on GitHub Pages">nav eligible</span>
          <% } else { %><span class="badge b-info" title="github.enabled=false → not eligible for GitHub Pages prev/next">nav n/a</span><% } %>
          <%# Phase 20260617-am-admin-validator-warning-badge-list-implementation-a：
              替換既有 warn def. placeholder 為 5 態 read-only validator warning badge；
              純消費 p.validationReport（pm-18 loader derive；report=git-ignored cache，validator 為 ground truth）；
              零 loader / reporter / validator 變更；不混 governance signals（gov badge 獨立）；
              不重算 rule；不 prescription；不 filter chip。 -%>
          <% var vr = p.validationReport || { reportAvailable: false, state: 'no-report', asOf: null }; %>
          <% if (!vr.reportAvailable || vr.state === 'no-report') { %>
            <span class="badge b-info" title="validation report 尚未產生或不可用；執行 npm run report:validation 後重整；warn ? 非 0 warnings">warn ?</span>
          <% } else if (vr.state === 'status-excluded') { %>
            <span class="badge b-info" title="status=<%= vr.status || '' %> 不在 validator universe〔ready/published〕；warn n/a 非 0 warnings">warn n/a</span>
          <% } else if (vr.state === 'clean') { %>
            <span class="badge b-ok" title="0 validator warnings (clean as of <%= vr.asOf || 'report' %>)；source: report-validation cache；validator 為 ground truth">warn ✓</span>
          <% } else if (vr.state === 'matched' && (vr.errorCount || 0) > 0) { %>
            <span class="badge b-missing" title="<%= vr.errorCount %> errors / <%= vr.warningCount %> warnings (as of <%= vr.asOf || 'report' %>)；source: report-validation cache；validator 為 ground truth；展開查看 byClass / issues">err <%= vr.errorCount %> warn <%= vr.warningCount %></span>
          <% } else if (vr.state === 'matched') { %>
            <span class="badge b-warn" title="<%= vr.warningCount %> validator warnings (as of <%= vr.asOf || 'report' %>)；source: report-validation cache；展開查看 byClass / issues">warn <%= vr.warningCount %></span>
          <% } else { %>
            <span class="badge b-info" title="unknown validationReport state — defensive fallback">warn ?</span>
          <% } %>
          <%# Phase 20260616-am-1-admin-suggested-fix-l2-readonly-ui-implementation-a：
              - per-post governance signal 摘要 badge（read-only；loader 已 derive 之 p.governanceSignals.signalSum）
              - signalSum > 0 → b-warn（黃；人眼可判斷之治理訊號）；= 0 → b-ok（皆已對齊）
              - 只顯示計數；不含 per-post prescription（「應改為 X」）；展開 row 看 Governance signals section -%>
          <% var govSum = (p.governanceSignals && p.governanceSignals.signalSum) || 0; %>
          <br><span class="badge <%= govSum > 0 ? 'b-warn' : 'b-ok' %>" title="taxonomy governance signals (derived, read-only)：unknown tag/category + cross-site mismatch 合計；展開查看明細。Admin 不自動修。"><% if (govSum > 0) { %>gov: <%= govSum %><% } else { %>gov ✓<% } %></span>
        </td>
        <td class="col-urls">
          <% if (p.blogger.publishedUrl) { %><div class="mono">📘 <a href="<%= p.blogger.publishedUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><%= p.blogger.publishedUrl %></a></div><% } %>
          <% if (p.github.previewUrl) { %><div class="mono">🐙 <a href="<%= p.github.previewUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><%= p.github.previewUrl %></a></div><% } %>
          <% if (!p.blogger.publishedUrl && !p.github.previewUrl) { %><span class="text-muted">(empty)</span><% } %>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="post-detail" data-idx="<%= idx %>" hidden>
        <td colspan="7">
          <%# Phase 20260522-night-3-e: missing metadata warning banner；重用既有 p.completeness.*；無 missing 時不渲染避免畫面太吵 -%>
          <%
            var missingList = [];
            if (p && p.completeness && typeof p.completeness === 'object') {
              if (p.completeness.seo === 'missing') missingList.push('SEO');
              if (p.completeness.fb === 'missing') missingList.push('FB metadata');
              if (p.completeness.blogger === 'missing') missingList.push('Blogger config');
              if (p.completeness.github === 'missing') missingList.push('GitHub config');
              if (p.completeness.url === 'missing') missingList.push('Output URL');
              if (p.completeness.categoryTags === 'missing') missingList.push('Category / Tags');
              if (p.completeness.fbPublished === 'missing') missingList.push('FB Published URL');
            }
          %>
          <% if (missingList.length > 0) { %>
          <div style="background: #fff4cc; border: 1px solid #f0d264; padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; font-size: 0.85em; color: #856404;">
            <strong>⚠️ Missing metadata：</strong>
            <ul style="margin: 0.25rem 0 0; padding-left: 1.25rem;">
              <% missingList.forEach(function(item) { %><li><%= item %></li><% }); %>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <% } %>
          <div class="detail-section">
            <h3>Identity</h3>
            <dl class="detail-grid">
              <dt>id</dt><dd class="mono"><%= p.id || '(empty)' %></dd>
              <dt>title</dt><dd><%= p.title || '(empty)' %></dd>
              <dt>titleEn</dt><dd><%= p.titleEn || '(empty)' %></dd>
              <dt>slug</dt><dd class="mono"><%= p.slug || '(empty)' %></dd>
              <dt>contentKind</dt><dd class="mono"><%= p.contentKind || '(empty)' %></dd>
              <dt>primaryPlatform</dt><dd class="mono"><%= p.primaryPlatform || '(empty)' %></dd>
              <dt>sourceSite</dt><dd class="mono"><%= p.sourceSite %></dd>
              <dt>status</dt><dd><%= p.status || '(empty)' %><% if (p.draft) { %> / draft=true<% } %></dd>
              <dt>category</dt><dd><%= p.category || '(empty)' %></dd>
              <dt>tags</dt><dd><% if (p.tags.length > 0) { p.tags.forEach(function(t) { %><span class="badge b-tag">#<%= t %></span><% }); } else { %>(empty)<% } %></dd>
            </dl>
          </div>

          <%# Phase 20260521-pm-59: Admin Platform Routing read-only section -%>
          <%# - 使用 pm-57 loader 新增之 canonicalTarget / platformUrl / gaHostname / githubStatus -%>
          <%# - 沿用既有 blogger / github 物件 + primaryPlatform；reuse 既有 badge class -%>
          <%# - 不含 utmPreviewUrl（pm-60 候選）/ platformMigrationNote（schema 未引入）-%>
          <div class="detail-section">
            <h3>Platform Routing</h3>
            <dl class="detail-grid">
              <dt>primaryPlatform</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.primaryPlatform === 'blogger') { %><span class="badge b-info">📘 blogger</span>
                <% } else if (p.primaryPlatform === 'github') { %><span class="badge b-ok">🐙 github</span>
                <% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing">(empty)</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>publishTargets</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.blogger.enabled) { %><span class="badge b-info">📘 blogger / <%= p.blogger.mode || '(no mode)' %></span><% } %>
                <% if (p.github.enabled) { %><span class="badge b-ok">🐙 github / <%= p.github.mode || '(no mode)' %></span><% } %>
                <% if (!p.blogger.enabled && !p.github.enabled) { %><span class="badge b-missing">(none enabled)</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>canonicalTarget</dt>
              <dd class="mono"><% if (p.canonicalTarget) { %><a href="<%= p.canonicalTarget %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><%= p.canonicalTarget %></a><% } else { %><span class="text-muted">—</span><% } %></dd>
              <dt>platformUrl</dt>
              <dd class="mono"><% if (p.platformUrl) { %><a href="<%= p.platformUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><%= p.platformUrl %></a><% } else { %><span class="text-muted">—</span><% } %></dd>
              <dt>gaHostname</dt>
              <dd class="mono" style="font-size: 0.85em;"><%= p.gaHostname || '—' %></dd>
              <dt>bloggerStatus</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.blogger.status === 'published') { %><span class="badge b-published"><%= p.blogger.status %></span>
                <% } else if (p.blogger.status) { %><span class="badge b-info"><%= p.blogger.status %></span>
                <% } else { %><span class="text-muted">(empty)</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>githubStatus</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.githubStatus === 'rendered') { %><span class="badge b-ok">rendered</span>
                <% } else if (p.githubStatus === 'pending') { %><span class="badge b-draft">pending</span>
                <% } else { %><span class="badge b-info">disabled</span><% } %>
              </dd>
            </dl>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em; margin: 0.25rem 0 0;">
              注：本 section 為 Admin read-only derived 顯示；不代表 sitemap / build / deploy 之實際審核結果。per <code>docs/admin-platform-routing-extension-plan.md</code>；不含 utmPreviewUrl（屬 pm-60 候選）/ platformMigrationNote（schema 未引入）。
            </p>
          </div>

          <%# Phase 20260615-night-3-admin-posts-index-readonly-derive-fields-a：Readiness 集中區
              - 五個 sub-block：Content / Navigation / GA4 / AdSense / Validation
              - 全部 read-only derived；不寫檔；不打 GA4·AdSense API；不重寫 validator
              - 不放 Apply / Save / Edit / Publish 按鈕；不偽稱已 live verified -%>
          <div class="detail-section">
            <h3>Readiness <span class="section-tag tag-readonly" style="font-size: 0.7em;">read-only · derived</span></h3>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.85em; margin: 0.1rem 0 0.5rem;">
              本區為 admin loader 從 frontmatter / settings 推導之 read-only 狀態快照；只反映 build-time
              可預期結果，<strong>不代表</strong> live deploy / Blogger / AdSense / GA4 後台之實際狀況。
              每個欄位皆附 source 與 note。
            </p>

            <%# --- Content readiness --- %>
            <h4 style="font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.4rem 0 0.2rem; color: #2c3e50;">Content readiness <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(derived)</span></h4>
            <dl class="detail-grid">
              <dt>title</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.contentReadiness && p.contentReadiness.titleExists) { %><span class="badge b-ok">present</span><% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing">missing</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>slug</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.contentReadiness && p.contentReadiness.slugExists) { %><span class="badge b-ok">present</span> <span class="mono"><%= p.slug %></span><% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing">missing</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>contentKind</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.contentReadiness && p.contentReadiness.contentKindExists) { %><span class="badge b-info"><%= p.contentKind %></span><% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing">missing</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>status / draft</dt>
              <dd>
                <% var srv = (p.contentReadiness && p.contentReadiness.statusValue) || ''; %>
                <% if (srv === 'ready') { %><span class="badge b-ready">ready</span>
                <% } else if (srv === 'draft' || (p.contentReadiness && p.contentReadiness.draftFlag)) { %><span class="badge b-draft">draft</span>
                <% } else if (srv === 'published') { %><span class="badge b-published">published</span>
                <% } else if (srv === 'archived') { %><span class="badge b-info">archived</span>
                <% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing"><%= srv || 'no status' %></span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>category / tags</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.contentReadiness && p.contentReadiness.categoryExists) { %><span class="badge b-info"><%= p.category %></span><% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing">no category</span><% } %>
                <span class="badge <%= (p.contentReadiness && p.contentReadiness.tagCount > 0) ? 'b-info' : 'b-missing' %>"><%= (p.contentReadiness && p.contentReadiness.tagCount) || 0 %> tag(s)</span>
              </dd>
            </dl>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em; margin: 0.1rem 0 0;">source: frontmatter (title / slug / contentKind / status / draft / category / tags)</p>

            <%# --- Navigation readiness --- %>
            <h4 style="font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.6rem 0 0.2rem; color: #2c3e50;">Navigation readiness <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(derived · template-level)</span></h4>
            <dl class="detail-grid">
              <dt>template-level nav</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.navReadiness && p.navReadiness.templateLevel === 'ready') { %>
                  <span class="badge b-ok">template-level ready</span>
                <% } else { %>
                  <span class="badge b-missing">unknown</span>
                <% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>eligible for prev/next (this post)</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.navReadiness && p.navReadiness.eligibleForNav) { %>
                  <span class="badge b-ok">eligible</span>
                  <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">(publishTargets.github.enabled = true)</span>
                <% } else { %>
                  <span class="badge b-info">not eligible</span>
                  <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">(publishTargets.github.enabled = false → 不會出現在 GitHub Pages prev/next 候選)</span>
                <% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>per-post live GA4 verified</dt>
              <dd>
                <span class="badge b-info">no</span>
                <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">admin 不抓 GA4 後台；live 事件須以 GA4 DebugView / Exploration 確認</span>
              </dd>
            </dl>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em; margin: 0.1rem 0 0;">source: <%= (p.navReadiness && p.navReadiness.source) || '(unknown)' %>；note: <%= (p.navReadiness && p.navReadiness.note) || '' %></p>

            <%# --- GA4 readiness (static config only) --- %>
            <h4 style="font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.6rem 0 0.2rem; color: #2c3e50;">GA4 readiness <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(derived · static-config)</span></h4>
            <dl class="detail-grid">
              <dt>ga4.enabled (global)</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.ga4Readiness && p.ga4Readiness.configEnabled) { %><span class="badge b-ok">true</span><% } else { %><span class="badge b-missing">false</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>measurementId</dt>
              <dd class="mono">
                <% if (p.ga4Readiness && p.ga4Readiness.hasMeasurementId) { %>G-…<%= p.ga4Readiness.measurementIdTail4 %><% } else { %><span class="empty">(none)</span><% } %>
                <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(masked tail4)</span>
              </dd>
              <dt>events registered</dt>
              <dd><%= (p.ga4Readiness && p.ga4Readiness.eventsRegistered) || 0 %></dd>
              <dt>surface indexable</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.ga4Readiness && p.ga4Readiness.surfaceIndexable === true) { %>
                  <span class="badge b-ok">indexable</span>
                <% } else if (p.ga4Readiness && p.ga4Readiness.surfaceIndexable === false) { %>
                  <span class="badge b-info">noindex</span>
                <% } else { %>
                  <span class="badge b-missing">unknown</span>
                <% } %>
                <% if (p.ga4Readiness && p.ga4Readiness.seoIndexingValue) { %>
                  <span class="text-muted mono" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(seo.indexing = <%= p.ga4Readiness.seoIndexingValue %>)</span>
                <% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>per-post event received</dt>
              <dd>
                <span class="badge b-info">unknown</span>
                <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">admin 不打 GA4 API / 不抓報表</span>
              </dd>
            </dl>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em; margin: 0.1rem 0 0;">
              source: <%= (p.ga4Readiness && p.ga4Readiness.source) || '(unknown)' %>；
              note: <%= (p.ga4Readiness && p.ga4Readiness.note) || '' %>
            </p>

            <%# --- AdSense readiness (per-post, two surfaces) --- %>
            <h4 style="font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.6rem 0 0.2rem; color: #2c3e50;">AdSense readiness <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(derived · resolve-adsense-blocks.js)</span></h4>
            <dl class="detail-grid">
              <dt>ads.enabled (global)</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.adsenseReadiness && p.adsenseReadiness.configEnabled) { %><span class="badge b-ok">true</span><% } else { %><span class="badge b-info">false</span><% } %>
                <% if (p.adsenseReadiness && p.adsenseReadiness.hasClient) { %>
                  <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(client present · masked)</span>
                <% } else { %>
                  <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(client missing)</span>
                <% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>post-level adsense</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (p.adsenseReadiness && p.adsenseReadiness.postLevelEnabled) { %><span class="badge b-ok">not opted out</span><% } else { %><span class="badge b-info">opted out (post.adsense.enabled=false)</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>block source</dt>
              <dd class="mono"><%= (p.adsenseReadiness && p.adsenseReadiness.overrideSource) || 'none' %></dd>
              <dt>resolved blocks · pages</dt>
              <dd>
                <% var pc = (p.adsenseReadiness && p.adsenseReadiness.pagesBlockCount) || 0; %>
                <span class="badge <%= pc > 0 ? 'b-ok' : 'b-info' %>"><%= pc %> block(s)</span>
              </dd>
              <dt>resolved blocks · blogger</dt>
              <dd>
                <% var bc = (p.adsenseReadiness && p.adsenseReadiness.bloggerBlockCount) || 0; %>
                <span class="badge <%= bc > 0 ? 'b-ok' : 'b-info' %>"><%= bc %> block(s)</span>
              </dd>
            </dl>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em; margin: 0.1rem 0 0;">
              source: <%= (p.adsenseReadiness && p.adsenseReadiness.source) || '(unknown)' %>；
              note: <%= (p.adsenseReadiness && p.adsenseReadiness.note) || '' %>。
              real client / slot id 只存於 <code>content/settings/ads.config.json</code>；本頁不顯示。
            </p>

            <%# --- Validation warnings (read-only consume of .cache/data/validation-report.json) ---
                Phase 20260616-admin-validation-report-detail-panel-readonly-consume-implementation-a：
                - 只讀 admin loader 注入之 p.validationReport（join validate:content reporter output；pm-14 §D）
                - report 缺檔 → 尚未產生；status-excluded（draft/archived，不在 validator universe）→ 未驗證（非 0）
                - matched → errorCount/warningCount/byClass/issue 簡列；ready/published 無 issue → 0 warnings(clean)
                - read-only：無 form/button/input/select/textarea/onclick/fetch；不修法、不 per-post prescription
                - 不取代 validator（ground truth 仍 npm run validate:content）；report 為 git-ignored cache（asOf 時點） -%>
            <% var vr = p.validationReport || { reportAvailable: false, state: 'no-report', asOf: null }; %>
            <h4 style="font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.6rem 0 0.2rem; color: #2c3e50;">Validation warnings <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(read-only · validate:content report)</span></h4>
            <% if (!vr.reportAvailable || vr.state === 'no-report') { %>
              <dl class="detail-grid">
                <dt>report</dt>
                <dd>
                  <span class="badge b-info">尚未產生</span>
                  <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">執行 <code>npm run report:validation</code> 後重新整理本頁</span>
                </dd>
              </dl>
            <% } else if (vr.state === 'status-excluded') { %>
              <dl class="detail-grid">
                <dt>狀態</dt>
                <dd>
                  <span class="badge b-info">未驗證</span>
                  <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">status=<%= vr.status || '' %>（draft/archived 不在 validator universe〔ready/published〕；非 0 warnings）</span>
                </dd>
              </dl>
            <% } else if (vr.state === 'clean') { %>
              <dl class="detail-grid">
                <dt>warnings</dt>
                <dd>
                  <span class="badge b-ok">0 warnings ✓</span>
                  <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">此文章未列於 report（ready/published 且無 issue）</span>
                </dd>
              </dl>
            <% } else if (vr.state === 'matched') { %>
              <dl class="detail-grid">
                <dt>errors / warnings</dt>
                <dd>
                  <span class="badge <%= (vr.errorCount > 0) ? 'b-missing' : 'b-warn' %>"><%= vr.errorCount %> error / <%= vr.warningCount %> warning</span>
                </dd>
                <dt>byClass</dt>
                <dd>
                  <% var bc = vr.byClass || {}; var bcKeys = Object.keys(bc).filter(function (k) { return (bc[k] || 0) > 0; }); %>
                  <% if (bcKeys.length === 0) { %>
                    <span class="text-muted">—</span>
                  <% } else { %>
                    <% bcKeys.forEach(function (k) { %><span class="badge b-warn" style="margin-right: 0.25rem;"><%= k %> × <%= bc[k] %></span><% }); %>
                  <% } %>
                </dd>
                <dt>issues（<%= vr.issueCount %>）</dt>
                <dd>
                  <% (vr.issues || []).forEach(function (it) { %>
                    <div style="font-size: 0.82em;"><span class="text-muted">[<%= it.severity %>]</span> <code><%= it.type %></code> <span class="text-muted">· <%= it.class %></span></div>
                  <% }); %>
                </dd>
              </dl>
            <% } %>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em; margin: 0.1rem 0 0;">
              <% if (vr.asOf) { %>report asOf：<%= vr.asOf %>（git-ignored cache，可能過時；validator 為 ground truth）。<% } else { %>validator 為 ground truth：<code>npm run validate:content</code>。<% } %>
              Admin 只顯示，不自動修；如要更新報表請重跑 <code>npm run report:validation</code>。
            </p>
          </div>

          <%# Phase 20260623-pm-sp7a-admin-readonly-page-metadata-summary-a：
              - additive read-only「Page metadata / 頁面中繼設定」collapsible section（接 loader 已 derive 之 p.pageMetadata）
              - 純顯示：<dl> + badge；無 input / select / textarea / Apply / button / onclick / fetch / form / 任何 write path
              - effective 值委派既有 SP-3/4a/5a helper（robots / listing / sitemap）；warning mirror SP-2 validator
              - 缺省欄位 → 顯示 default / current behavior（非 error）；不進 Missing metadata banner
              - gatedDownload / platformPolicy 只顯示 safe 欄位（mechanism / postSubmitResource / 平台名+indexing/listings）；
                **永不**顯示 secret / token / 表單回覆 / 私有 URL（loader 端已只投影 safe 欄位）
              - <details> 預設 closed；summary 顯示 effective 一行（索引 · 列表 · sitemap）+ 任何 warning badge
              - validator（npm run validate:content）仍為 ground truth；本區 warning 為 read-only mirror 提示 -%>
          <% var pm = p.pageMetadata || {}; %>
          <% var pmPt = pm.pageType || { raw: '', present: false, valid: null, label: 'article (default)' }; %>
          <% var pmSeo = pm.seoIndexing || { value: '', indexable: null, source: '' }; %>
          <% var pmRobots = pm.robots || { value: 'index, follow', source: 'default' }; %>
          <% var pmList = pm.includeInListings || { rawLabel: 'auto', effective: true }; %>
          <% var pmMap = pm.includeInSitemap || { rawLabel: 'auto', effective: true, eligible: true }; %>
          <% var pmFeeds = pm.includeInFeeds || { rawLabel: 'auto', hasConsumer: false }; %>
          <% var pmGated = pm.gatedDownload || { present: false, isObject: false, mechanism: '', postSubmitResource: '', suspiciousKeys: [] }; %>
          <% var pmPp = pm.platformPolicy || { present: false, isObject: false, platforms: [] }; %>
          <% var pmWarn = Array.isArray(pm.warnings) ? pm.warnings : []; %>
          <% var pmIdxLabel = (pmSeo.indexable === true) ? '可收錄' : (pmSeo.indexable === false ? '不收錄' : '未知'); %>
          <details class="detail-section">
            <summary style="cursor: pointer;">
              <h3 style="display: inline; border-bottom: none;">Page metadata / 頁面中繼設定 <span class="section-tag tag-readonly" style="font-size: 0.7em;">read-only · derived</span></h3>
              <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">[索引: <%= pmIdxLabel %> · 列表: <%= pmList.effective ? '顯示' : '隱藏' %> · sitemap: <%= pmMap.effective ? '納入' : '排除' %>]</span>
              <% pmWarn.forEach(function (w) { %><span class="badge b-warn" style="margin-left: 0.25rem;">⚠️ <%= w.badge %></span><% }); %>
            </summary>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.85em; margin: 0.3rem 0 0.5rem;">
              本區為 admin loader 從 frontmatter 推導之 read-only 索引/列表政策快照；effective 值委派
              既有 page-type-robots / include-in-listings / include-in-sitemap helper，<strong>不</strong>由 Admin 另算。
              缺省欄位顯示 default / current behavior（非告警）。
            </p>
            <dl class="detail-grid">
              <dt>頁面類型 / Page type</dt>
              <dd>
                <span class="badge <%= (pmPt.valid === false) ? 'b-warn' : 'b-info' %>"><%= pmPt.label %></span>
                <% if (pmPt.valid === false) { %><span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">(非合法列舉值；validator 以 page-type-invalid warn)</span><% } else if (!pmPt.present) { %><span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">(缺省視為一般文章)</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>搜尋引擎索引 / Indexing</dt>
              <dd>
                <span class="badge <%= (pmSeo.indexable === true) ? 'b-ok' : (pmSeo.indexable === false ? 'b-info' : 'b-missing') %>"><%= pmIdxLabel %></span>
                <span class="text-muted mono" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(seo.indexing = <%= pmSeo.value || '—' %>, source: <%= pmSeo.source %>)</span>
              </dd>
              <dt>robots meta (effective)</dt>
              <dd>
                <span class="badge <%= (pmRobots.value === 'index, follow') ? 'b-ok' : 'b-info' %>"><%= pmRobots.value %></span>
                <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(source: <%= pmRobots.source %>)</span>
              </dd>
              <dt>顯示於列表 / Listings</dt>
              <dd>
                <span class="badge <%= pmList.effective ? 'b-ok' : 'b-info' %>"><%= pmList.effective ? '顯示' : '隱藏' %></span>
                <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">raw: <%= pmList.rawLabel %> → effective: <%= pmList.effective %></span>
              </dd>
              <dt>加入 sitemap / Sitemap</dt>
              <dd>
                <span class="badge <%= pmMap.effective ? 'b-ok' : 'b-info' %>"><%= pmMap.effective ? '納入' : '排除' %></span>
                <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">raw: <%= pmMap.rawLabel %> → effective: <%= pmMap.effective %></span>
                <% if (!pmMap.eligible) { %><br><span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(legacy contentKind:download / noindex safety；與 listing 正交)</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>加入 feeds / Feeds</dt>
              <dd>
                <span class="badge b-info"><%= pmFeeds.rawLabel %></span>
                <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(feed 未啟用 · no consumer)</span>
              </dd>
              <dt>受控下載 / Gated download</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (!pmGated.present) { %>
                  <span class="text-muted">—</span>
                <% } else { %>
                  <span class="badge b-info">gated download</span>
                  <% if (pmGated.mechanism) { %><span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">mechanism: <%= pmGated.mechanism %></span><% } %>
                  <% if (pmGated.postSubmitResource) { %><span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">· resource: <%= pmGated.postSubmitResource %></span><% } %>
                  <% if (pmGated.suspiciousKeys && pmGated.suspiciousKeys.length > 0) { %><br><span class="badge b-warn">敏感 key: <%= pmGated.suspiciousKeys.join(', ') %></span> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(只列 key 名；value 不顯示／不應入 repo)</span><% } %>
                <% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>平台覆寫 / Platform policy</dt>
              <dd>
                <%# SP-9a：display-only effective hint。raw 顯示 + effective hint 分兩行。
                    🔴 仍是顯示用：本欄之 effective 值**不**影響 robots / listing / sitemap / canonical /
                       feeds / Blogger guidance / live output。Blogger Google Form gated download 仍須
                       Blogger 後台人工 noindex。真消費屬 SP-9b / SP-9c（dormant 待 Dean 批准）。 -%>
                <% if (!pmPp.present) { %>
                  <span class="text-muted">— (全平台沿用頂層值)</span>
                <% } else if (!pmPp.isObject) { %>
                  <span class="badge b-warn">型別非法</span> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">(validator 以 page-platform-policy-invalid-type warn)</span>
                <% } else { %>
                  <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em; margin: 0 0 0.25rem;">
                    raw = 作者原填值；effective = SP-9a 解析後預期值（<strong>display-only</strong>；目前**不**改 robots / listing / sitemap / canonical / feeds / Blogger guidance 任一輸出；真消費屬 SP-9b/9c，dormant）。
                  </p>
                  <% pmPp.platforms.forEach(function (pf) { %>
                    <% var pfEi = pf.effectiveIndexing || { value: null, source: 'absent', topLevelFallback: null }; %>
                    <% var pfEl = pf.effectiveIncludeInListings || { value: null, source: 'absent', topLevelFallback: null }; %>
                    <% var nameBadgeClass = pf.secretLike ? 'b-warn' : (pf.recognized ? 'b-info' : 'b-warn'); %>
                    <div style="font-size: 0.82em; margin-bottom: 0.35rem;">
                      <span class="badge <%= nameBadgeClass %>"><%= pf.name %></span>
                      <% if (pf.secretLike) { %>
                        <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.95em;">⚠️ 平台 key 命中敏感名單；value 不顯示 / 不應入 repo（SP-8 warn）。</span>
                      <% } else if (!pf.recognized) { %>
                        <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.95em;">⚠️ 非建議 platform key（建議 github / blogger / future；SP-8 warn）。raw 仍列出供除錯，effective 不推導。</span>
                      <% } %>
                      <%# indexing 行：raw + effective hint -%>
                      <div style="margin-left: 1rem;">
                        <span class="text-muted">indexing</span>
                        <span class="text-muted">· raw: </span><code><%= pf.indexing || '—' %></code>
                        <span class="text-muted">· effective: </span>
                        <% if (pfEi.source === 'override') { %>
                          <span class="badge b-info"><%= pfEi.value %></span>
                          <span class="text-muted">(override)</span>
                        <% } else if (pfEi.source === 'inherit') { %>
                          <span class="badge b-info">inherit → <%= pfEi.topLevelFallback || '—' %></span>
                          <span class="text-muted">(top-level fallback)</span>
                        <% } else if (pfEi.source === 'invalid') { %>
                          <span class="badge b-warn">invalid</span>
                          <span class="text-muted">(validator warn；不推導)</span>
                        <% } else if (pfEi.source === 'secret') { %>
                          <span class="badge b-warn">secret</span>
                          <span class="text-muted">(不讀 value)</span>
                        <% } else if (pfEi.source === 'unrecognized-platform') { %>
                          <span class="badge b-warn">— (platform 未認可)</span>
                        <% } else { %>
                          <span class="text-muted">— (未填，沿用頂層 <%= pfEi.topLevelFallback || '—' %>)</span>
                        <% } %>
                      </div>
                      <%# includeInListings 行 -%>
                      <div style="margin-left: 1rem;">
                        <span class="text-muted">includeInListings</span>
                        <span class="text-muted">· raw: </span><code><%= (pf.includeInListings === null) ? '—' : pf.includeInListings %></code>
                        <span class="text-muted">· effective: </span>
                        <% if (pfEl.source === 'override') { %>
                          <span class="badge b-info"><%= pfEl.value %></span>
                          <span class="text-muted">(override)</span>
                        <% } else if (pfEl.source === 'inherit') { %>
                          <span class="badge b-info">inherit → <%= (pfEl.topLevelFallback === null) ? '—' : pfEl.topLevelFallback %></span>
                          <span class="text-muted">(top-level fallback)</span>
                        <% } else if (pfEl.source === 'invalid') { %>
                          <span class="badge b-warn">invalid</span>
                          <span class="text-muted">(validator warn；不推導)</span>
                        <% } else if (pfEl.source === 'secret') { %>
                          <span class="badge b-warn">secret</span>
                          <span class="text-muted">(不讀 value)</span>
                        <% } else if (pfEl.source === 'unrecognized-platform') { %>
                          <span class="badge b-warn">— (platform 未認可)</span>
                        <% } else { %>
                          <span class="text-muted">— (未填，沿用頂層 <%= (pfEl.topLevelFallback === null) ? '—' : pfEl.topLevelFallback %>)</span>
                        <% } %>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  <% }); %>
                <% } %>
              </dd>
              <% if (pmWarn.length > 0) { %>
              <dt>危險組合 / Warnings</dt>
              <dd>
                <% pmWarn.forEach(function (w) { %><div style="font-size: 0.82em;"><span class="badge b-warn"><%= w.badge %></span> <code><%= w.type %></code> <span class="text-muted">· <%= w.message %></span></div><% }); %>
              </dd>
              <% } %>
            </dl>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em; margin: 0.1rem 0 0;">
              source: frontmatter + page-type-robots / include-in-listings / include-in-sitemap helpers。
              note: read-only 推導快照；Admin 不修改 frontmatter；warning 為 SP-2 validator 之 mirror，
              ground truth 為 <code>npm run validate:content</code>。
            </p>
          </details>

          <%# Phase 20260616-am-1-admin-suggested-fix-l2-readonly-ui-implementation-a：
              - additive per-post Governance signals section（read-only；接 loader 已 derive 之 p.governanceSignals）
              - 只列計數 / flag + sample 訊號；不含 per-post prescription（「應改為 X」）；不含 form / button / input / select / textarea / fetch
              - 含 anti-write 一句話 + 治理 docs cross-link（沿用 slice-1 / bucket-note 樣板）
              - empty state（signalSum===0）→ 正向確認「皆已對齊」
              - source 明示 admin loader（含 draft / 所有 status）vs validator（ready/published）範圍差異 -%>
          <div class="detail-section">
            <h3>Governance signals <span class="section-tag tag-readonly" style="font-size: 0.7em;">read-only · derived</span></h3>
            <% var gs = p.governanceSignals || { unknownTagCount: 0, unknownCategoryFlag: false, crossSiteMismatchTagCount: 0, crossSiteMismatchCategoryFlag: false, signalSum: 0 }; %>
            <% if ((gs.signalSum || 0) === 0) { %>
              <p style="margin: 0.1rem 0 0.4rem;"><span class="badge b-ok">✓ 皆已對齊</span> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.85em;">本篇 tags / category 皆在 registry 內，且 site 與 sourceSite 對齊；無 unknown / cross-site mismatch 訊號。</span></p>
            <% } else { %>
              <p style="margin: 0.1rem 0 0.4rem;"><span class="badge b-warn">⚠️ <%= gs.signalSum %> 個治理訊號</span> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.85em;">下列為人眼可判斷之 taxonomy 訊號；Admin 不自動修。</span></p>
            <% } %>
            <dl class="detail-grid">
              <dt>unknown tag(s)</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if ((gs.unknownTagCount || 0) > 0) { %><span class="badge b-warn"><%= gs.unknownTagCount %></span> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">tag 未在 <code>tags.json</code> 定義</span>
                <% } else { %><span class="badge b-ok">0</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>unknown category</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (gs.unknownCategoryFlag) { %><span class="badge b-warn">yes</span> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">category 未在 <code>categories.json</code> 定義</span>
                <% } else { %><span class="badge b-ok">no</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>cross-site mismatch · tag(s)</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if ((gs.crossSiteMismatchTagCount || 0) > 0) { %><span class="badge b-warn"><%= gs.crossSiteMismatchTagCount %></span> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">tag.site 不含本文 sourceSite（<%= p.sourceSite %>）</span>
                <% } else { %><span class="badge b-ok">0</span><% } %>
              </dd>
              <dt>cross-site mismatch · category</dt>
              <dd>
                <% if (gs.crossSiteMismatchCategoryFlag) { %><span class="badge b-warn">yes</span> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">category.site 不含本文 sourceSite（<%= p.sourceSite %>）</span>
                <% } else { %><span class="badge b-ok">no</span><% } %>
              </dd>
            </dl>

            <%# Phase 20260616-admin-governance-aggregation-detail-panel-readonly-ui-implementation-a：
                - additive read-only governanceAggregation summary（接 loader 已 derive 之 p.governanceAggregation；pm-4）
                - 與上方 raw 4-signal dl 同源（皆衍生自 governanceSignals）；保留 raw dl 不刪、不改語意
                - 純唯讀：無 button / input / form / onclick / handler / filter / badge-link / write path
                - 非 validator warning count；validator warnings 仍 deferred（見上方 Validation warnings 區段）
                - empty（hasSignals false / signals[] 空）→ 正向 fallback，不 render error
                - 沿用既有 class（.detail-grid / .badge / .b-warn / .b-ok / .text-muted）+ 既有 inline-style 排版慣例，不新增 CSS -%>
            <% var ga = (p.governanceAggregation && typeof p.governanceAggregation === 'object') ? p.governanceAggregation : { hasSignals: false, totalSignalCount: 0, byClass: {}, signals: [] }; %>
            <% var gaSignals = Array.isArray(ga.signals) ? ga.signals : []; %>
            <% var gaByClass = (ga.byClass && typeof ga.byClass === 'object') ? ga.byClass : {}; %>
            <% var gaCrossSite = gaSignals.filter(function (s) { return s && typeof s.type === 'string' && s.type.indexOf('cross-site-mismatch') === 0; }).reduce(function (a, s) { return a + (Number(s.count) || 0); }, 0); %>
            <h4 style="font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.6rem 0 0.2rem; color: #2c3e50;">Aggregation summary <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em;">(read-only · derived; same-source)</span></h4>
            <dl class="detail-grid">
              <dt>hasSignals</dt>
              <dd><span class="badge <%= ga.hasSignals ? 'b-warn' : 'b-ok' %>"><%= ga.hasSignals ? 'yes' : 'no' %></span></dd>
              <dt>totalSignalCount</dt>
              <dd><span class="badge <%= (ga.totalSignalCount || 0) > 0 ? 'b-warn' : 'b-ok' %>"><%= ga.totalSignalCount || 0 %></span></dd>
              <dt>byClass · taxonomy</dt>
              <dd>
                <span class="badge <%= (gaByClass.taxonomy || 0) > 0 ? 'b-warn' : 'b-ok' %>"><%= gaByClass.taxonomy || 0 %></span>
                <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">其中 cross-site mismatch：<%= gaCrossSite %></span>
              </dd>
            </dl>
            <% if (gaSignals.length > 0) { %>
              <p style="margin: 0.1rem 0 0.3rem; font-size: 0.85em;"><span class="text-muted">signals（固定順序 type · class × count）：</span>
                <% gaSignals.forEach(function (s) { %><span class="badge b-warn" style="margin-right: 0.3rem;"><%= s.type %> · <%= s.class %> × <%= s.count %></span><% }); %>
              </p>
            <% } else { %>
              <p style="margin: 0.1rem 0 0.3rem; font-size: 0.85em;"><span class="badge b-ok">無治理訊號</span> <span class="text-muted">signals[] 為空。</span></p>
            <% } %>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em; margin: 0.1rem 0 0.4rem;">
              此 summary 來自既有 per-post <code>governanceSignals</code> / <code>governanceAggregation</code>（同源；含 draft / 所有 status），<strong>非 validator warning count</strong>；validator warnings 改由上方 Validation warnings 區段<strong>讀取 <code>validate:content</code> 之 generated report</strong>（<code>.cache/data/validation-report.json</code>，read-only consume）呈現（見上方區段）。
            </p>

            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em; margin: 0.1rem 0 0;">
              source: admin loader（<code>derivePostGovernanceSignals</code>；含 draft / 所有 status；以 sourceSite 判斷 site mismatch）。
              <strong>Admin 不自動修</strong>；請手改 frontmatter / <code>tags.json</code> / <code>categories.json</code> 後執行 <code>npm run validate:content</code>。
              validator 範圍為 ready / published（過濾 draft）→ 與本區（含 draft）計數可能不對齊，屬設計。
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.78em; margin: 0.2rem 0 0;">
              治理決策參考：
              <a href="../docs/20260615-admin-content-taxonomy-governance-preanalysis.md" rel="noopener"><code>docs/20260615-admin-content-taxonomy-governance-preanalysis.md</code></a> ·
              <a href="../docs/20260616-admin-suggested-fix-readonly-ui-preanalysis.md" rel="noopener"><code>docs/20260616-admin-suggested-fix-readonly-ui-preanalysis.md</code></a>
            </p>
          </div>

