            <p style="font-size: 0.82em; color: #555; margin: 0.25rem 0 0.5rem;">支援欄位（per <code>docs/admin-2-write-pre-analysis.md</code> §4.1 safe editable subset）：description / searchDescription / titleEn / coverAlt</p>
            <%# Phase 20260527-night-9 Admin Write Infra Phase 3b dry-run-only UI
