  </p>

  <%# Phase 20260627-admin-markdown-export-ui-preflight-hardening-a:
      Draft-only contract callout — non-interactive, scannable summary of what
      `New post draft` export does and does NOT do. Wording mirrors the
      constants + invariants locked by check:admin-markdown-export
      (TARGET_FOLDERS / VALIDATION_COMMAND / status:"draft" + draft:true).
