            <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">→ 只填中段段名（不含 date、不含 .md、不含完整路徑）；lowercase kebab-case，例 <code>test-title</code>；系統自動組 <code>{date}-{slug}.md</code>；不合法時 Download 按鈕會 disable</span>
            <%# Phase 20260701-admin-slug-suggestion-helper-slice-a:
                Display-only slug suggestion strip — derives a kebab-case
                candidate from titleEn > title (mirrored by
