          <td style="padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;">
            <input type="date" id="npd-date" style="padding: 0.2rem; font-family: inherit;">
            <button type="button" id="npd-today" style="padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.25rem; font-family: inherit;" title="填入本機今天日期">今天</button>
            <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">→ YYYY-MM-DD；首次載入自動填本機今天；按右側「今天」可重填為本機今天</span>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; vertical-align: top;"><label for="npd-category">category</label></td>
          <td style="padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;">
            <select id="npd-category" style="padding: 0.25rem; font-family: inherit;">
              <%# Phase 20260701-admin-category-select-site-aware-options-a:
                  Site-aware category select. Initial paint filters to the default
                  site (github) so a fresh GitHub draft only offers github-allowed
                  categories (currently tech-note). The inline renderCategoryOptions(site)
                  rebuilds these options when #npd-site changes — preserving a still-valid
                  choice or falling back to the first available category for the new site.
                  Registry-bound options only (no free text) per smoke #156-157; mirrors
                  the tag datalist default-github filter. -%>
              <%
                var npdCatDefaultSite = 'github';
                var sysCats = (sys && sys.categories && Array.isArray(sys.categories.list)) ? sys.categories.list : [];
                sysCats.forEach(function(c) {
                  var cid = typeof c.id === 'string' ? c.id : '';
                  if (cid === '') return;
                  var cSiteArr = Array.isArray(c.site) ? c.site : [];
                  if (cSiteArr.length > 0 && cSiteArr.indexOf(npdCatDefaultSite) < 0) return;
                  var cname = typeof c.name === 'string' ? c.name : cid;
                  var csites = cSiteArr.join('/');
                  var clabel = csites ? (cid + ' — ' + cname + ' [' + csites + ']') : (cid + ' — ' + cname);
              %>
                <option value="<%= cid %>"><%= clabel %></option>
              <% }); %>
            </select>
            <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">→ 來源 <code>categories.json</code>；依目前 <code>site</code> 只列出該 site 合法的 category（github 目前為 <code>tech-note</code>），切換 site 會重建並自動選該 site 第一個可用 category；draft export 不擋，Ready preflight 仍會顯示 <code>unknown-category</code> / <code>category-site-mismatch</code> warning（與 tags 一致）</span>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; vertical-align: top;"><label for="npd-tags">tags</label></td>
