            <%# Phase 20260627-admin-category-tag-registry-hints-implementation-a:
                datalist hint —— 從 tagUsage.perTag 取得 registry-defined tag ids（含 unused），
                以瀏覽器原生 datalist 提供 autocomplete 提示。新增 tag 仍允許 free text；
                不在 registry 的 tag 會在 Ready preflight 顯示 unknown-tag warning。
                不使用 picker component / 不引入新 dependency。 -%>
            <input type="text" id="npd-tags" list="npd-tags-options" placeholder="comma-separated；空白會 trim、重複會去除" style="width: 100%; padding: 0.25rem; box-sizing: border-box;" autocomplete="off">
            <datalist id="npd-tags-options">
              <%# Phase 20260629-admin-tag-picker-site-aware-options-a:
                  Initial paint filters to the default site (github) so the
                  autocomplete suggestions match the form's default site=github
                  and Dean is not offered Blogger-only tags (book / reading-notes…)
                  on a GitHub draft. The inline renderTagOptions(site) rebuilds
                  this datalist when #npd-site changes. Free text stays allowed
                  (input type=text) — datalist is hint-only, never a strict select. -%>
              <%
                var npdRegTags = (typeof tagUsage === 'object' && tagUsage && Array.isArray(tagUsage.perTag)) ? tagUsage.perTag : [];
                var npdDefaultSite = 'github';
                npdRegTags.forEach(function(t) {
                  var tid = typeof t.id === 'string' && t.id ? t.id : (typeof t.slug === 'string' ? t.slug : '');
                  if (tid === '') return;
                  var tsiteArr = Array.isArray(t.site) ? t.site : [];
                  if (tsiteArr.length > 0 && tsiteArr.indexOf(npdDefaultSite) < 0) return;
                  var tsites = tsiteArr.join('/');
                  var tlabel = tsites ? (tid + ' [' + tsites + ']') : tid;
              %>
                <option value="<%= tid %>" label="<%= tlabel %>"></option>
              <% }); %>
            </datalist>
            <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em;">→ 例：<code>github, vite, static-site</code>；datalist 依目前 <code>site</code> 列出 <code>tags.json</code> 中該 site 合法的 tag id（僅輔助提示、非硬性限制；新 tag 不會自動寫入 <code>tags.json</code>），不在清單內仍可手動輸入（Ready preflight 會顯示 unknown-tag / site-mismatch warning）</span>
            <%# Phase 20260701-admin-tag-registry-inline-hint-slice-c1:
                Inline registry hint below the tags input — mirrors the tags-only
                subset of analyzeRegistryHints(input, REGISTRY_SNAPSHOT) so the
                author sees unknown-tag / tag-site-mismatch feedback right by the
                field, not only in the Ready preflight aggregate. DISPLAY-ONLY:
                does NOT gate export (契約仍 status:"draft" + draft:true), does
                NOT change #npd-ready-registry-hints (Ready preflight aggregate
                still lists the full hint set — no dedupe), does NOT touch the
                tags datalist / #npd-category. Empty tags → hidden via
                display:none (no layout jump). No READY / PASS wording —
                describes registry alignment only. -%>
            <div id="npd-tags-registry-hint" aria-live="polite"
                 style="display: none; margin-top: 0.2rem; font-size: 0.78em;"></div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <%# Phase 20260701-admin-site-registry-reference-display-slice-b:
            Read-only reference block — lists the categories / tags that are valid
            for the currently selected #npd-site, so Dean can see the legal registry
            values up-front (before mistyping a tag or picking a cross-site category).
            DISPLAY-ONLY helper: no <input> / <select> / name — it never enters
            recompute() or the export, does NOT constrain the free-text #npd-tags,
            and does NOT turn the registry-bound #npd-category <select> into free
            text. Same registry sources as the site-aware datalist / category select
            (sys.categories.list + tagUsage.perTag); it does NOT write tags.json /
            categories.json. Initial paint = default site (github); the inline
            renderSiteRegistryReference(site) rebuilds #npd-site-registry-ref when
            #npd-site changes (additive listener; does not touch CAT_EL / the tags
            datalist / PRIM_EL / recompute). -%>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2" style="padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem 0.5rem;">
            <div class="npd-site-registry-ref-wrap" style="background: #fff; border: 1px dashed #c5d6e8; border-radius: 4px; padding: 0.5rem 0.65rem; font-size: 0.8em;">
              <div style="font-weight: 600; color: #1f2d3d; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">目前 <code>site</code> 合法 category / tag 參考
                <span class="section-tag tag-readonly" style="font-size: 0.72em; font-weight: 500; margin-left: 0.3rem;">read-only</span>
              </div>
              <div id="npd-site-registry-ref">
                <%
                  var npdRefSite = 'github';
                  var npdRefCats = (sys && sys.categories && Array.isArray(sys.categories.list)) ? sys.categories.list : [];
                  var npdRefTags = (typeof tagUsage === 'object' && tagUsage && Array.isArray(tagUsage.perTag)) ? tagUsage.perTag : [];
                  var npdRefCatParts = [];
                  npdRefCats.forEach(function(c) {
                    var cid = (typeof c.id === 'string' && c.id) ? c.id : (typeof c.slug === 'string' ? c.slug : '');
                    if (cid === '') return;
                    var csite = Array.isArray(c.site) ? c.site : [];
                    if (csite.length > 0 && csite.indexOf(npdRefSite) < 0) return;
                    var cname = (typeof c.name === 'string' && c.name) ? c.name : cid;
                    npdRefCatParts.push(csite.length ? (cid + ' — ' + cname + ' [' + csite.join('/') + ']') : (cid + ' — ' + cname));
                  });
                  var npdRefTagParts = [];
                  npdRefTags.forEach(function(t) {
                    var tid = (typeof t.id === 'string' && t.id) ? t.id : (typeof t.slug === 'string' ? t.slug : '');
                    if (tid === '') return;
                    var tsite = Array.isArray(t.site) ? t.site : [];
                    if (tsite.length > 0 && tsite.indexOf(npdRefSite) < 0) return;
                    npdRefTagParts.push(tsite.length ? (tid + ' [' + tsite.join('/') + ']') : tid);
                  });
                %>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;"><strong>categories：</strong><%= npdRefCatParts.length ? npdRefCatParts.join('、') : '（此 site 無合法 category）' %></div>
                <div><strong>tags：</strong><%= npdRefTagParts.length ? npdRefTagParts.join('、') : '（此 site 無合法 tag）' %></div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-muted" style="margin-top: 0.3rem; font-size: 0.95em;">僅供參考；<code>[scope]</code> 為該項適用的 site。此區塊<strong>不會自動寫入</strong> <code>categories.json</code> / <code>tags.json</code>，也不限制自由輸入（<code>category</code> 仍為 registry-bound <code>&lt;select&gt;</code>、<code>tags</code> 仍可自由輸入）。</div>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
