  <%# === AdSense（read-only，masked） === -%>
  <section class="admin-section" aria-labelledby="adsense-h">
    <h2 id="adsense">AdSense <% if (sys && sys.ads && sys.ads.enabled) { %><span class="section-tag tag-live">enabled</span><% } else { %><span class="section-tag tag-dormant">disabled</span><% } %> <span class="section-tag tag-readonly">read-only</span></h2>
    <p class="section-lede">real client / slot id 只儲存於 <code>content/settings/ads.config.json</code>，本頁僅以 tail4 遮罩顯示。<strong>不要</strong>在本頁貼上完整 client / slot id。master kill-switch 由 <code>ads.enabled</code> 控制。</p>
